## Product locks (v0.2 — do not reopen without user ask)

- Hosting: **public HTTPS** (domain + Cloudflare); **internet required**
- **No** classroom AP / offline LAN / mkcert-for-class as product path
- Primary check-in: **tripod station** — teacher phone scans **student personal QR**
- Student phone: identify → confirm → **display** QR (no student board-scan camera)
- Auto codes from server time vs session `T0`; unopened stay blank; end → missing `0`
- Excel remains gradebook; app captures + exports
- **No** student password accounts; no face ID / geofence / SSO in v0.2
- Presence board optional (names/counts only — **no** rotating check-in QR)

## Engineering norms

- Prefer deleting dead paths in the same change as the replacement (see `18-v0.2-remove-overhaul.md`)
- Pure functions for scoring (`lib/scoring`) with unit tests
- Server time only for check-in timestamps
- Do not expand to multi-tenant SaaS in this phase
- Git: see `git-commits.mdc` — no push until user asks; conventional commits when committing
